data.description: Stunning custom home in a cul-de-sac within Lovejoy ISD with many remodeled areas and updates! The kitchen, remodeled in 2019, showcases top of the line appliances & finishes. Hand-scraped oak floors add a touch of elegance and warmth. The primary bedroom has French doors leading to the hot tub and a recently refreshed bathroom for a spa-like experience. The custom office with built-in double desks is a perfect dedicated workspace. Two grand living areas downstairs offers plenty of space for gatherings. The recently updated upstairs includes a third flexible living room, 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. Updates include new carpet and bathrooms with new sinks, counters, tile, showers, and faucets. The outdoor area includes a pool, hot tub, firepit, covered patio, and a spacious backyard. The large outdoor gazebo kitchen is equipped with a 32-in Teppanyaki grill, sink, and ample bar top space. The property includes a three-car garage and circular driveway for convenient parking.
